    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Welcome to Music Lab!\r\n\r\nThis is a lab that lets you combine **coding** and **music**! This level is all about exploration! Try clicking things! Try dragging things! Explore this space! \r\n\r\nSee how many of these you can do:\r\n\r\n- Drag out a block [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-id:play_sound_at_current_location_simple2)\r\n- Connect two blocks [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=id:when-run-block)\r\n- Play a track [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=run-button)\r\n- Change the track\r\n- Play 3 tracks in a row: Beat, Bass, Lead.\r\n- Change the order of your tracks\r\n- Change where the song starts playing in the timeline\r\n- Delete a block\r\n- Clear the workspace and start over\r\n- Play 3 tracks simultaneously\r\n\r\n",
